===================================================
Create a logic print a new string made of 3 copies of the last 2 chars of the original string.

      Hint: The string length will be at least 2.

===================================================

Given a string, if the string begins with "red" or "blue" print that color string, otherwise print the empty string.

                 input :"redxx" → "red"
                 input :"xxred" → ""
                 input :"blueTimes" → "blue"

===================================================
Given a string, return a "rotated left 2" version where the first 2 chars are moved to the end.
     Hint: The string length will be at least 2.

                 input :"Hello" -> "lloHe"
                 input :"java" → "vaja"
                 input :"Hi" → "Hi"




